headline: Apogee Enterprises (APOG) Tops Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Apogee Enterprises (APOG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +12.00% and +7.08%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
